edu.uth.clamp.config

Class ConfigUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uth.clamp.config.ConfigUtil

  • public class ConfigUtil
extends Object
    util class for nlp components, using java reflecting to scan all the available nlp components and their dependency; all the available processors and their default parameters; save or load setting to or from IFile; create UI widgets;.
    Author:
    jwang16, esoysal
